- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the proposed model uses attention mechanisms to predict human trajectories. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes a new approach to human trajectory prediction. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is relevant as the paper deals with modeling social interactions between humans in a crowd.
